22:07.994 --> 22:10.795
Tell officer hogan
to hold off on the riot gear.

22:10.797 --> 22:11.929
Stand up! Fight back!

22:11.931 --> 22:13.097
No more black men
under attack!

22:16.002 --> 22:18.069
Why did you meet
with the governor of new mexico?

22:18.071 --> 22:19.520
Because governor martinez

22:19.521 --> 22:20.970
Has been outspoken
on this clarence parker mess.

22:20.973 --> 22:22.006
I wanted to hear
her thoughts.

22:22.008 --> 22:23.808
I know a vetting
when i see one.

22:23.810 --> 22:25.943
You and cyrus were giving her
the once-over for v.P.

22:25.945 --> 22:27.812
Cyrus thought
it would be a good idea.

22:27.814 --> 22:29.847
That does not mean she's
the right person for the job.
You told me

22:29.849 --> 22:31.982
You were gonna pick
someone boring and unelectable.

22:31.984 --> 22:33.901
I prostituted myself

22:33.902 --> 22:35.819
So that you would get
your mistress back,

22:35.822 --> 22:38.889
And now you're gonna take
someone young and charismatic

22:38.891 --> 22:40.858
And female and latina

22:40.860 --> 22:43.861
And make her the vice president
of the united states?

22:43.863 --> 22:44.829
How dare you?

22:44.831 --> 22:45.996
What happened to my turn?

22:45.998 --> 22:48.065
[ sighs ]

22:50.036 --> 22:52.903
We had a deal, fitz.

22:57.009 --> 22:58.142
Crowd:
Stand up! Fight back!

22:58.144 --> 23:00.845
No luck
on the surveillance tapes?

23:00.847 --> 23:02.330
Nothing faces the street

23:02.331 --> 23:03.814
Except for the bank,
and i just found out

23:03.816 --> 23:05.416
The police were there
last night,

23:05.417 --> 23:07.017
And they took the tapes,
the backups -- everything.

23:07.019 --> 23:08.819
The dcpd
has been sitting on footage

23:08.821 --> 23:10.104
Of the shooting all day?

23:10.105 --> 23:11.388
If they haven't released it yet,
that means --

23:11.391 --> 23:14.024
It didn't happen
the way they said it did.

23:14.026 --> 23:15.860
I can't help you.
I wish i could.

23:15.862 --> 23:17.128
I need to see that tape,
david.

23:17.130 --> 23:18.896
I need to see
what happened!

23:18.898 --> 23:20.798
I'm assuming you were hired
by the metro police.

23:20.800 --> 23:22.133
Maybe just -- i don't know --
ask them for a copy.

23:22.135 --> 23:23.868
I can't.
You can't?

23:23.870 --> 23:25.920
I quit.
Quit, or were you fired?

23:25.921 --> 23:27.971
David.
I can't just go marching
into every sensitive situation

23:27.974 --> 23:29.039
Trying to rush
the justice process.

23:29.041 --> 23:31.008
There are laws, okay?

23:31.009 --> 23:32.976
Ones i'm being paid by
the u.S. Government to uphold.

23:32.979 --> 23:34.812
To protect people
who look like you!

23:34.814 --> 23:36.080
Oh, come on, liv!

23:36.082 --> 23:38.115
You talk about fairness
and justice

23:38.117 --> 23:39.950
Like it's available
to everybody!

23:39.952 --> 23:40.985
It's not!

23:40.987 --> 23:43.988
That man standing over
his son's body

23:43.990 --> 23:46.824
Thinks he knows
he's going to end up

23:46.826 --> 23:48.025
In one of two places --

23:48.027 --> 23:50.895
A jail cell
or a drawer in the morgue.

23:50.897 --> 23:53.831
And to hell
if i can't look him in the eye

23:53.833 --> 23:55.099
And tell him he's wrong.

23:55.101 --> 23:57.034
I can't fix this, david!

23:57.036 --> 24:01.005
I-i have nothing left,
no more tricks in my bag.

24:01.007 --> 24:02.106
It's too much!

24:02.108 --> 24:04.975
It's too...

24:07.079 --> 24:09.013
You're exhausted.

24:09.015 --> 24:11.816
After everything
you've just been through,

24:11.818 --> 24:14.118
This is the last thing
you should be dealing with.

24:34.140 --> 24:36.974
I thought
i was going to die.

24:39.111 --> 24:45.082
For about a week straight,
i thought i was a goner.

24:45.084 --> 24:49.153
I lived
in complete and total fear.

24:49.155 --> 24:51.155
I know.

24:51.157 --> 24:57.127
Imagine feeling like that
every single day of your life.

25:01.033 --> 25:03.067
[ sighs ]

25:06.105 --> 25:08.172
What is it you want?

25:08.174 --> 25:10.908
A subpoena.

25:10.910 --> 25:12.910
[<i> camera shutter clicking</i> ]

